    <abstract>
      <t>The CoAP protocol was designed with direct connections and proxies in mind. This document defines mechanisms by which chains of proxies can be set up. In combination, they enable the operation of hidden services and client similar to how Tor (The Onion Router) enables it for TCP based protocols.</t>
